    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扩展你的吸血鬼巢穴</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/64e449b231696bf633d0844a6feb33b8.poster.avif?t=1758285795\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/64e449b231696bf633d0844a6feb33b8.webm?t=1758285795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>通过解锁新的房间和楼层来建造并扩展你的城堡。每一次扩展都会为你的吸血鬼提供新的能力提升机会，并解锁额外的游戏功能。<br><i>在试玩版中，你可以在入门级别体验基本的城堡扩展系统，并探索一个专门为本版本准备的区域。</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >释放血之魔法</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/7886edae6b111fa2eb0c8669c0c5cc48.poster.avif?t=1758285795\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/7886edae6b111fa2eb0c8669c0c5cc48.webm?t=1758285795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>作为吸血鬼，运用血之魔法与人类和怪物战斗。从敌人身上吸取的鲜血会为你的吸血鬼敏捷度提供能量 —— <strong>时间静止（Chronostasis）</strong>。这一独特技能能让敌人心生绝望 —— 使用时会让敌人瞬间冻结，而你与同伴吸血鬼则能以难以想象的速度发动攻击。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操控多个吸血鬼</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/521301187caad97b894da4f430c09e75.poster.avif?t=1758285795\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/521301187caad97b894da4f430c09e75.webm?t=1758285795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在 <i>Vampire Clans</i> 中，狩猎将变得更加具有策略性，因为你可以同时操控多达三名吸血鬼，每个吸血鬼都有自己独特的技能组合。在进入战斗前，你需要为他们选择最佳的战术和专精。玩家可以随时切换吸血鬼，并向其他角色下达指令。时间静止系统让多角色管理更加直观，你可以减缓时间并精确规划攻击。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >潜行还是战斗？</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/c76d2ecabcfe3dad78fc14e2d44323a2.poster.avif?t=1758285795\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/c76d2ecabcfe3dad78fc14e2d44323a2.webm?t=1758285795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>并非每一场战斗都需要正面迎击。阴影是你最大的盟友。利用潜行和训练有素的蝙蝠来追踪猎物，或逐一消灭成群的敌人。巧妙地避免被发现，可以让你在不进行正面战斗的情况下击败对手。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >复杂的氏族政治</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/c95d91d06cdc1259105c46c7aaaf5bca.poster.avif?t=1758285795\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/c95d91d06cdc1259105c46c7aaaf5bca.webm?t=1758285795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><i>Vampire Clans</i> 的世界充满了敌对吸血鬼氏族之间的政治阴谋。这些派系为权力而战，互相袭击前哨并在街头交锋。政治系统允许你建立联盟或树立对手，从而塑造你的旅程。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为巴黎的瘟疫</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/c4c861bf63aa78823205ea169fcdf6d6.poster.avif?t=1758285795\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871190/extras/c4c861bf63aa78823205ea169fcdf6d6.webm?t=1758285795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>踏入一个广阔的、非线性的世界，其灵感来源于 19 世纪的巴黎。地图被划分为多个区域，既指引你的探索，也显示敌人的难度。随着你逐步深入城市，敌人会变得愈发强大，需要你不断提升角色才能生存下去。这种开放世界的设计带来了丰富的 RPG 体验，让探索既充满回报又暗藏危险。",
